headline: 2 High-Yield Energy Stocks to Buy With $1,000 and Hold Forever
summary: The energy sector is highly volatile, a fact that has been on clear display of late.  Most investors should focus on owning reliable industry giants like dividend stalwart Chevron.  Conservative high-yield investors should sidestep the volatility with a midstream giant like Enterprise Products Partners.

headline: Investing $25,000 in These 2 Warren Buffett Stocks Will Generate $1,200 in Annual Passive Income
summary: Dividend stocks can generate reliable passive income.  Looking for stocks in Warren Buffett's portfolio is never a bad idea.  Strong dividends can also make it more worthwhile to invest in a turnaround story.
